1
00:00:19,233 --> 00:00:24,744
September 21, 1945.
That was the night I died.

2
00:00:56,334 --> 00:00:58,305
Damn tramps.

3
00:00:58,605 --> 00:01:00,115
Watch it!

4
00:01:00,926 --> 00:01:02,286
Disgusting!

5
00:01:02,346 --> 00:01:03,747
Is he dead?

6
00:01:03,847 --> 00:01:05,977
The Americans'll be arriving
any day now.

7
00:01:06,087 --> 00:01:08,859
It's disgraceful,
having these bums here!

8
00:01:18,001 --> 00:01:19,922
<i>Mama...!</i>

9
00:01:21,462 --> 00:01:24,642
What day is it?

10
00:01:35,307 --> 00:01:37,497
Setsuko...

11
00:01:47,561 --> 00:01:49,241
Another one.

12
00:02:03,224 --> 00:02:04,806
What is this stuff?

13
00:02:05,056 --> 00:02:08,027
Never mind. Just dump it!

14
00:02:20,090 --> 00:02:22,651
This one's a goner, too.

15
00:02:22,751 --> 00:02:25,452
You can see it in their eyes.

16
